    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>CISCO EXPANDING IN INDIA</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By P.J. Anthony</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Anthony, P J</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Cisco Systems Inc will invest $150 million over next two years to expand its Indian research and development operations in Bangalore, making them Cisco's largest outside US; Cisco has invested $75 million in India since 1996 (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Seeking to further benefit from India's growing prominence in high-technology industries, Cisco Systems Inc., the leading maker of computer equipment for the Internet, said it would invest $150 million over the next two years to expand its Indian research and development operations in Bangalore, making them Cisco's largest outside of the United States. Cisco, based in San Jose, Calif., has invested $75 million in India since 1996.</p>
        <p>P. J. Anthony (NYT)</p>
      </block>
